ent-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721&d=ajJRCbjZ3CJF8zdY8%2Fu%2F151eSlELYVUX4DDX6cHIoDA%3D&h=3ace7067\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721</a>"},{"pid":"691a10588c47d222497c4f9a211fbe698fff9bbe","tid":1374235,"uid":167883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:08:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73da4058323642adb25a07bef834a145d440f11f","tid":1374235,"uid":206176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:12:14.000Z","msg":"屌得好"},{"pid":"41a1250cd988d0b20527f44ebacfe341644d1257","tid":1374235,"uid":77461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:15:18.000Z","msg":"你班垃圾警犬叫司長下台問左你老細一哥<br />\n<br />\n有時真係駁唔到既說話<br />\n例如呢篇野講到警權過大<br />\n屈穎妍屌班狗 係有料就唔撈先屌"},{"pid":"4bde341ee077df6bf8e4852aa06757c1ce39f507","tid":1374235,"uid":280452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:15:33.000Z","msg":"過程係爽<br />\n但標題完全錯熬哂 你無撚野呀<br />\n仲要條友只係自稱<br />\n自high 下算喇"},{"pid":"8b0f597a59725874dc5d36be0562f9471f06c8a4","tid":1374235,"uid":268976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:18:11.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"7ed610c1cb725244bd38f2147010b75d9e468dcb","tid":1374235,"uid":87687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:21:31.000Z","msg":"雖然是自high , 不過都係一篇好文. <br />\n稍嫌鞋油多了一點."},{"pid":"371f1148cf8624ac818d1497994ce57ddd55ef71","tid":1374235,"uid":48057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:21:37.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"9e32468b56d56afd06f4c9b3061f70b361231b65","tid":1374235,"uid":51349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":